@node "Cheat" "IUC solution"

@{fg shine} Solution to Innocent Until Caught@{fg text}

FIRST PLANET ---

space port:

take passport from the bench
go out
go to the other side (left and up)

bar:

talk with drunk man (ask him how he ern money in this dump)
take his pawn ticket from his pocket
take jar and cover (on the left table)
use cover on jar
go out
go left to the pawn shop

pawn shop:

give ticket to receive camera
examine vase to receive silver cover of bubble gum
go out
go throw ally

ally:

pick up hose bag and can of coke
go left

snack bar:

use camera on power outlet (to charge it)
get oil can
go back to ally

ally:

use camera on homeless
get hat
examine hat (to receive money)
go to pawn shop

pawn shop:

get vase
use vase with bag
get out
go to hooker home PARADISE

hooker home:

give guard passport (then he will let you in)
give vase to madam
ask her to give something in return
take the statue and the perfume from the table
get the walking stick from the floor
wait until the resepianict put bubble gum on the counter
take the bubble gum (yuck)
get out
go to the snack bar

snack bar:

give statue to biker
talk to him (ask him to lend you his friend coat)
examine garbage (you will find an egg) (yepee I always wanted an old egg)
go to the bar

bar:

sit on the left chair
order drink
give him money (then you will see a fight)
get ring from the floor
use silver cover of bubble gum on coin
go out
go to the subway (near the pawn shop)

subway :

use coin on gate
enter subway (you will see a machine with a screw in it)
use oil on screw (I think that should do it)
get screw
go left and take the radio
go to the bar

bar:

talk to robot
use screw on robot
take printed card
use printed card with radio (now you have a remote control can it
operates my TV ?)
go to the snack bar

snack bar:

go to the harbor

harbor:

get close to the boat and use remote control on robot (he walks away yeeee)
get sailor hat from the railing
go back to the pawn shop

pawn shop:

give hat to receive a rag
talk with the pawn man (until he says that he will think about it)
give him the ring (to receive a mission)
go to subway

subway:
enter to the train (hey wait for me)
take pressure air can
use hose on air can
go down at the second stop
go to art gallery

art gallery:

get ball from statue
use carpet on the center statue
use ball on air can (now you will have a target cross (please 
don't shot please)
aim on the glass of the statue (you will crack it but not enough)
get the ball and use it again with the air can (now the statue will fall)
get statue
go to subway

subway:
go back to pawn shop (three stations if I'm not mistaking)

pawn shop:

give statue to pawn man
go to subway

subway:

drive to gorgie St. (three stations if I'm not mistaking)

gorgie St.:
use jar on sausage stand (you will get a mion inside the jar YUCK I HATE 
THIS)
get hot dog
use jar on fly (you will catch him inside)
go to police station

police station:

talk to police man (to get a flower bag)
get the flower bag
go out
go to the bank

