@node "ur2" "Advent"

@{fg shine} Advent V1.0@{fg text}

 Well it's that time again and this program is nearly out of use
for another year but its still a pretty nice idea. Of course,
it's an Advent Calender for the Amiga so it saves you having to
buy one.

 Each day when you boot up your computer you will be presented with
the advent calender and that days door will open to reveal the picture.
In the background there is a huge picture of a snowman to make
the whole program nicer. You will need to have a battery backed up
clock in your Amiga otherwise the program will tell you that it
is not December yet.

 A nice little program to get into the spirit of things, although
only useful once a year, but it's still a nice idea. The only problem
is you don't get any chocolates :( hehe!

