@node "ur4" "SwosTED"

@{fg shine} SwosTED 3.0@{fg text}

 If you've read the review of the Swos '97/'98 updater in the
games section you'll know that SWOS is one of my favourite
games on any platform. This is a util to help make SWOS just
that little bit better and something that Sensible Software
should have built in themselves but, oh well, they didn't. Luckily
though we have other SWOS enthusiasts that are dedicated to
making your life easier and thats were SwosTED 3.0 steps in.

 SwosTED as you may have guessed by the name is a team editor
for Sensible World Of Soccer, it has been programmed in Amos
Pro 2.0 and seems to work nicely and without any problems at
all. The data is loaded quickly and the teams can be edited
easyly with a few clicks of a button you can make Man Utd
have the worst team like they should have ;) (Ed- Lets see
how many angry Man U supporters that sparks off :) hehe)
and Arsenal with the best speed, finishing and anything. If
you think that a player should be a certain nationality then
just pick the nationality you want and it'll be changed.
Click a few more buttons and you can make Dennis Bergkamp
have brown hair and be a goalkeeper.

 Once you have made all your alterations click on Accept then
pack it into SWOS data format which is built in and save. Now
you can load up Sensi and find yourself as a £15m star striker
for Barcelona. Good eh? Well not only that.... all you have to
do is send the author an email with a few comments and you
get a registration key.

 Overall this is a great little package, although let down by
the fact that there is no WB interface and you have to put
up with the Amos style of interface, it's still great anyhow!

