@{b}From@{ub} : Heinrik Jhonson, Canada (hreardon@stemnet.calvin.nf.ca)

 Hi all at AIO team!
        I think that Gateway 2000 shoud market the Amiga more and
i would very much like to see advert on televisions to make people
more aware of the Amiga presence. Apart from that I think that
the amiga has a winning formula. how about making some more games.
Thanks for the mag and I really like the interviews, especially
